title: Tigers' Norris says he kept pitching with cancerous growth (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,385 Tigers' Norris says he kept pitching with cancerous growth (Yahoo Sports) DETROIT (AP) -- Tigers left-hander Daniel Norris says he kept pitching last season after finding out he had a cancerous growth on his thyroid.
